content: I can just summarize the main points from the webinar, since my notes are a bit messy. One of the key takeaways was the importance of conducting thorough keyword research to understand what terms my target audience is searching for. The presenter also emphasized the need to optimize my meta tags, titles, and descriptions to make my content more discoverable. Another point that stuck with me was the importance of creating high-quality, engaging content that provides value to my readers.
